  "siteName": "ByteByteGo Newsletter",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"body markup\" dir=\"auto\">\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">\n    <br>\n   </h2>\n   <p>This week’s system design refresher:</p>\n   <ul>\n    <li>\n     <p>10 Key Data Structures We Use Every Day</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>🚀 New Launch: Become an AI Engineer | Learn by Doing | Cohort 2!</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>IP Address Cheat Sheet Every Engineer Should Know</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Which Protocols Run on TCP and UDP</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Why is DeepSeek-OCR such a BIG DEAL?</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>SPONSOR US</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">10 Key Data Structures We Use Every Day\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://blog.bytebytego.com/i/177690588/key-data-structures-we-use-every-day\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Fxka!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60f07f90-6f22-4b1f-ab2e-d98e8ccc755a_3000x3900.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Fxka!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60f07f90-6f22-4b1f-ab2e-d98e8ccc755a_3000x3900.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1893\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/60f07f90-6f22-4b1f-ab2e-d98e8ccc755a_3000x3900.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1893,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"Image\" title=\"Image\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <ul>\n    <li>\n     <p>list: keep your Twitter feeds</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>stack: support undo/redo of the word editor</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>queue: keep printer jobs, or send user actions in-game</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>hash table: cashing systems</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Array: math operations</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>heap: task scheduling</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>tree: keep the HTML document, or for AI decision</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>suffix tree: for searching string in a document</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>graph: for tracking friendship, or path finding</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>r-tree: for finding the nearest neighbor</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>vertex buffer: for sending data to GPU for rendering</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p>Over to you: Which additional data structures have we overlooked?</p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">🚀 New Launch: Become an AI Engineer | Learn by Doing | Cohort 2!\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://blog.bytebytego.com/i/177690588/new-launch-become-an-ai-engineer-learn-by-doing-cohort\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p>After the incredible success of our first cohort (almost 500 people attended), I’m thrilled to announce the launch of Cohort 2 of Become an AI Engineer!</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gvn0!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1cf44858-3c91-429e-91ed-f91902ba00da_2360x2920.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!gvn0!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1cf44858-3c91-429e-91ed-f91902ba00da_2360x2920.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1801\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1cf44858-3c91-429e-91ed-f91902ba00da_2360x2920.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1801,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"Image\" title=\"Image\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>This is not just another course about AI frameworks and tools. Our goal is to help engineers build the foundation and end to end skill set needed to thrive as AI engineers.</p>\n   <p>Here’s what makes this cohort special:</p>\n   <ul>\n    <li>\n     <p>Learn by doing: Build real world AI applications, not just by watching videos.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Structured, systematic learning path: Follow a carefully designed curriculum that takes you step by step, from fundamentals to advanced topics.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Live feedback and mentorship: Get direct feedback from instructors and peers.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Community driven: Learning alone is hard. Learning with a community is easy!</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p><span>We are focused on skill building, not just theory or passive learning. Our goal is for every participant to walk away with a strong foundation for building AI systems.</span>\n    <br>\n    <br>\n    <span>If you missed Cohort 1, now’s your chance to join us for Cohort 2.</span></p>\n   <p data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://bit.ly/3LfXki3&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Check it out here&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\" class=\"button-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/3LfXki3\" rel=\"\" class=\"button primary\"><span>Check it out here</span></a></p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">IP Address Cheat Sheet Every Engineer Should Know\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://blog.bytebytego.com/i/177690588/ip-address-cheat-sheet-every-engineer-should-know\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Nizo!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffa24eaf-4fc7-4278-a0df-faddb41c765f_2048x2662.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!Nizo!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fffa24eaf-4fc7-4278-a0df-faddb41c765f_2048x2662.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1893\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ffa24eaf-4fc7-4278-a0df-faddb41c765f_2048x2662.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1893,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"Image\" title=\"Image\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Which Protocols Run on TCP and UDP\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://blog.bytebytego.com/i/177690588/which-protocols-run-on-tcp-and-udp\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p>Every message sent over the internet has two layers of communication, one that carries the data (transport) and one that defines what the data means (application). TCP and UDP sit at the transport layer, but they serve completely different purposes.</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ZdF6!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fef416976-ae0f-48f5-86e1-0189c0b9be88_2360x2664.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ZdF6!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fef416976-ae0f-48f5-86e1-0189c0b9be88_2360x2664.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1644\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ef416976-ae0f-48f5-86e1-0189c0b9be88_2360x2664.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1644,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"Image\" title=\"Image\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>TCP is connection-oriented. It guarantees delivery, maintains order, and handles retransmission when packets get lost.</p>\n   <ul>\n    <li>\n     <p>HTTP runs on TCP. The browser opens a TCP connection, sends an HTTP request, waits for the HTTP response, and closes the connection (or keeps it alive for subsequent requests). Every web page you have ever loaded used this pattern.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>HTTPS adds TLS over TCP. The TCP connection happens first. Then comes the TLS handshake with public key exchange, session key negotiation, and finally encrypted data transfer.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>SMTP uses TCP for email. Messages flow from sender to SMTP server to receiver over TCP connections. Email can’t afford to lose data mid-transmission, so TCP’s reliability is essential.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p>UDP is connectionless. No handshake. No guaranteed delivery. No order preservation. Just fire data requests and responses into the network and hope they arrive. Sounds chaotic, but it’s fast.</p>\n   <ul>\n    <li>\n     <p>HTTP/3 runs over QUIC, which uses UDP. This seems backwards until you realize QUIC reimplements the reliability features of TCP inside UDP, but with better performance. Multiple streams over one connection. Built-in TLS 1.3. Faster connection establishment. The numbered streams in the diagram show parallel data flows that don’t block each other.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p>Over to you: What tools do you use to analyze transport layer performance?</p>\n   <p>Existing LLMs struggle with long inputs because they can only handle a fixed number of tokens, known as the context window, and attention cost grows quickly as inputs get longer.</p>\n   <p>DeepSeek-OCR takes a new approach.</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!dzxT!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc11356c8-c512-4e1f-81c7-1f895fd38307_2360x2920.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n       <picture><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!dzxT!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc11356c8-c512-4e1f-81c7-1f895fd38307_2360x2920.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1801\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c11356c8-c512-4e1f-81c7-1f895fd38307_2360x2920.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1801,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;Image&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"Image\" title=\"Image\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\">\n           <path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>Instead of sending long context directly to an LLM, it turns it into an image, compresses that image into visual tokens, and then passes those tokens to the LLM.</p>\n   <p>Fewer tokens lead to lower computational cost from attention and a larger effective context window. This makes chatbots and document models more capable and efficient.</p>\n   <p>How is DeepSeek-OCR built? The system has two main parts:</p>\n   <ol>\n    <li>\n     <p>Encoder: It processes an image of text, extracts the visual features, and compresses them into a small number of vision tokens.</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Decoder: A Mixture of Experts language model that reads those tokens and generate text one token at a time, similar to a standard decoder-only transformer.</p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p>When to use it?</p>\n   <p>DeepSeek-OCR shows that text can be efficiently compressed using visual representations.</p>\n   <p>It is especially useful for handling very long documents that exceed standard context limits. You can use it for context compression, standard OCR tasks, or deep parsing, such as converting tables and complex layouts into text.</p>\n   <p>Over to you: What do you think about using visual tokens to handle long-context problems in LLMs? Could this become the next standard for large models?</p>\n   <h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\"><strong>SPONSOR US</strong>\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\">\n      <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://blog.bytebytego.com/i/177690588/sponsor-us\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\">\n       <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\">\n        <path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path>\n       </svg>\n      </button>\n     </div>\n    </div></h2>\n   <p>Get your product in front of more than 1,000,000 tech professionals.</p>\n   <p>Our newsletter puts your products and services directly in front of an audience that matters - hundreds of thousands of engineering leaders and senior engineers - who have influence over significant tech decisions and big purchases.</p>\n   <p>Space Fills Up Fast - Reserve Today</p>\n   <p><span>Ad spots typically sell out about 4 weeks in advance. To ensure your ad reaches this influential audience, reserve your space now by emailing </span><strong>sponsorship@bytebytego.com.</strong></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文简要介绍了 DeepSeek-OCR，其创新之处在于使用视觉标记扩展 LLM 上下文窗口。文章中还穿插了简短的技术回顾和多个广告。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文简要介绍了 DeepSeek-OCR，其创新之处在于使用视觉标记扩展 LLM 上下文窗口。文章中还穿插了简短的技术回顾和多个广告。",
  "summary": "提供的内容是一份技术通讯，其中混合了简短的技术回顾，主要是关于数据结构、IP 地址和 TCP/UDP 协议的图解速查表，以及 QA Wolf 和 AI 工程课程的广告。最详细的技术部分介绍了 DeepSeek-OCR，这是一种解决 LLM 上下文窗口限制的创新方法。DeepSeek-OCR 通过将长文本输入转换为视觉标记来压缩信息，降低计算成本，并有效扩展上下文窗口。其架构包括一个用于视觉特征提取的编码器和一个用于文本生成的混合专家解码器。这种方法因其在处理长篇文档、执行标准 OCR 任务以及深度解析复杂布局方面的实用性而备受关注。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "DeepSeek-OCR 通过将长输入转换为视觉令牌来解决 LLM 上下文窗口的限制，从而降低了注意力成本并扩大了有效上下文。",
      "explanation": "DeepSeek-OCR 有效地减少了 LLM 处理的令牌数量，从而降低了计算开销。同时，它也显著扩大了有效的上下文窗口，提高了模型的能力和效率。"
    },
    {
      "point": "DeepSeek-OCR 的架构包括一个用于视觉特征压缩的编码器和一个用于文本生成的混合专家解码器。",
      "explanation": "该系统首先使用编码器从文本图像中提取和压缩视觉特征，生成视觉令牌。然后，这些令牌被传递给一个仅使用解码器的 Transformer 模型，具体来说是一个混合专家模型，以生成最终的文本输出。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该方法有利于处理非常长的文档、标准 OCR 和复杂布局的深度解析。",
      "explanation": "DeepSeek-OCR 特别适用于处理超出典型 LLM 上下文限制的文档，执行标准的光学字符识别，以及从复杂的视觉布局（如表格）中提取结构化信息。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "现有的 LLM 在处理长输入时会遇到困难，因为它们只能处理固定数量的令牌，即上下文窗口，并且随着输入长度增加，注意力机制的计算成本也随之迅速上升。",
    "DeepSeek-OCR 并非直接将长文本发送给 LLM，而是先将其转换为图像，再压缩为视觉令牌，然后传递给 LLM。",
    "更少的令牌可以降低注意力的计算成本，并扩大有效的上下文窗口。这使得聊天机器人和文档模型更强大、更高效。"
  ],
